name: The Stoned Relic Faces Of MetaBert

metadata.name: Mystical Bert
metadata.description:
These stoned relic faces of MetaBert have been found throughout the world.  The legend of Bert goes deeper than one may think.  This collection was made with the help of a very sophisticated A.I. to bring you the most accurate representations of the actual stone relic faces.

One of the most evil leaders to ever rule over the kingdom this Bert is known for his dark magic!
